---
const INDICATORS = [
  ["Practice Tenure", "6+", "Years"],
  ["Global SAP Projects", "20+", "Indicative"],
  ["Enterprise Clients", "10+", "Fortune 500"],
  ["Coverage Markets", "8", "EU · APAC · NA"],
  ["Tax Solutions", "12+", "DRC · Taxware · Peppol"],
  ["Languages", "3", "KO · EN · JA"],
];
---
<section id="about" class="section section--subtle">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-12 about-grid">
      <div class="about-text-col reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">02 · About</p>
        <h2 class="h-1">신뢰를 바탕으로<br />혁신을 이끕니다.</h2>
        <p class="lead measure about-lead">
          도상은 글로벌 SAP S/4HANA 컨설팅과 자체 솔루션 사업을 동시에 영위하는 정예 컨설팅 펌입니다.
          작은 규모로 깊은 전문성을 유지하며, 정확하고 검증 가능한 결과만을 약속합니다.
        </p>
        <p class="measure about-body">
          "SAP Stability, Powered by AI and FinTech" — 안정성을 기반으로 AI와 FinTech 영역의 새로운 가치를 창출합니다.
          Fortune 500을 포함한 글로벌 기업의 핵심 시스템 전환·Tax Compliance·디지털 자산 회계 자동화를 수행해 왔습니다.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-data-col reveal">
        <div class="about-data-card">
          <div class="eyebrow about-data-eyebrow">Practice Indicators (Indicative)</div>
          <dl class="about-data-list">
            {INDICATORS.map(([label, val, note]) => (
              <div class="about-data-row">
                <dt>{label}</dt>
                <dd><span class="about-data-val">{val}</span><span class="about-data-note">{note}</span></dd>
              </div>
            ))}
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid { gap: 64px; align-items: start; }
  .about-text-col { grid-column: span 7; }
  .about-data-col { grid-column: span 5; }
  .about-lead { margin: 24px 0 24px; }
  .about-body { font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text); }
  .about-data-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 32px; background: var(--color-bg);
  }
  .about-data-eyebrow { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .about-data-list { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .about-data-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    align-items: baseline; gap: 16px;
    padding: 16px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .about-data-row:first-child { border-top: 0; padding-top: 0; }
  .about-data-row dt {
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-weight: 500;
  }
  .about-data-row dd {
    margin: 0; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-navy); display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px;
  }
  .about-data-val { font-weight: 500; font-size: 16px; color: var(--color-navy); }
  .about-data-note {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  @media (max-width: 1023px) {
    .about-text-col, .about-data-col { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .about-grid { gap: 48px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-data-card { padding: 24px; }
  }
</style>
